ygData.messageBody:
I'd worry more about dying in level 31.....
In hell levels, the exp you lose from dying is barely noticable.. but in the
level afterwards, you stand to lose a bubble of exp (yellow) with each
death.

Trust me, i got 3 yellow bubbles into 31, so i say to my group, lets try
drachnids in FV, well i died 3 times in a row trying to get my corpse, and
undinged back into hell, luckily there was a 57 cleric nice enough to ress
all 3 corpses :)


Qaelan
